<scenario>
The agent A provided the following violation scenario:
Inside MHD_stop_daemon, the code iterates over daemon->worker_pool and calls MHD_stop_daemon(&daemon->worker_pool[i]); This is a direct call to the same function from within itself (even though different daemon instances are passed), i.e. direct recursion, which violates MISRA C 2023 Rule 17.2 (functions shall not call themselves, directly or indirectly).
</scenario>

